data.description: Perched against the stunning backdrop of the front range and the iconic Air Force Academy, this residence redefines luxury living with breathtaking views and thoughtful upgrades. it invites those with a discerning eye to shape their own unique living experience. Revel in sweeping vistas of the front range, enhanced by the distinguished silhouette of the Air Force Academy. Vaulted ceilings grace the living room, adding an extra dimension of openness and sophistication to the heart of the home. The kitchen, a culinary haven, boasts a built-in espresso machine, adding a touch of indulgence to your daily routine. The foyer and hallway introduce rich oak hardwood floors, seamlessly transitioning into the warmth of engineered hardwood throughout—a harmonious blend of classic and contemporary styles. An additional 2-car attached garage enhances the property's utility, providing even more space for your vehicles and storage needs. Extensive asphalt driveways, complete with extra lined-parking spaces, ensure convenience and space for all your parking needs. Less than an hour to Denver International Airport and an easy commute to Colorado Springs, this residence offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Beyond the 6-car garage, discover a dedicated RV storage area and adjacent RV parking with essential hookups, allowing for seamless integration of your on-the-road adventures. The heated workshop not only facilitates projects with radiant heating and epoxy coating but also includes a large conference room with a loft above it—a versatile space for work or leisure. Enjoy peace of mind with a state-of-the-art 2023-installed septic system, a brand-new well pump, newer roof, and stucco, ensuring a solid foundation for worry-free living. While many areas shine with modern updates, some await your personal touch— imprint your style and elevate the home to truly make it your own!
